WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.199 --> 00:00:03.620
&gt;&gt; HOST: The garbage in the landfill is built
up in layers

00:00:03.620 --> 00:00:06.180
until each shell is filled.

00:00:06.180 --> 00:00:08.890
After the garbage has been spread and compacted,

00:00:08.890 --> 00:00:09.940
it gets covered up with sand.

00:00:10.940 --> 00:00:13.190
Let's go!

00:00:25.940 --> 00:00:29.190
[truck noises]

00:00:34.940 --> 00:00:38.190
[music]

00:00:51.940 --> 00:00:56.940
[big bump trucks moving the sand around the
landfill]

00:01:17.310 --> 00:01:19.310
[trucks beeping as they reverse]

00:01:48.810 --> 00:01:54.810
[bulldozers spreading out the sand to cover
the garbage]

00:02:29.109 --> 00:02:34.109
[huge dump trucks being filled with sand]

00:03:20.999 --> 00:03:31.999
[sand pouring out of dump trucks which is then spread over garbage with huge bulldozers]

00:04:06.900 --> 00:04:10.900
[big bump trucks pouring out sand]

